{"type": "article", "id": 15022, "title": "Bauhaus Stool", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-17T08:45:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 20, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000337MaRxgD3vLKmP9dOb.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这把椅子使用了方形、三角形、圆形三个组件并分别对应红、黄、蓝三原色的边，非常巧妙。木质的组件类似于积木，在设计上有简洁的北欧的风，也引人探究。除了功能上是一把椅子外，它也可以当做一个巧妙的装饰品。在墙上安置一个插口，就可以把三个组件挂起来。这把折叠椅子需要自己组装，因而也方便携带。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142401v7By8niM5lDx06wP.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142402YAnzGm7eIPZkS1jf.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142403mMq2lxveVKnufbSE.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142404VwLcoNj3RAbIq4Ge.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142404gU2hf4taQDJVoO8b.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1620\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}